result.name: HERE is a PUB

reviews.text: Cute little pub that is out of the way. The music selection was great and just loud enough. The cocktails were good too. And there is a rice set or 3 at each table to give you something to do while waiting for the fish & chips.

This place is scamming people out of money. They were all too quick to offer the buy one, get one free deal without letting us know the condition that there’s minimum order for each person and you need to pay for the overpriced snack(peanut) which you didn’t order.
Overpriced, poor pizza. Beer was pricy (even for HK) but tasty. Good service.
a place to chill w/ wine and iconic cocktail i love!!!
Service just so so

reviews.text: Shop is opposite to a sheesha place JOOBA and its inside building on 6th floor. Owner was really helpful. Essential for hooka lover
staff are always not there
My girlfriend and I’ve been looking to buy a sheesha in hk for ages…finally found Hookah Hutt… Apparently they’re the only ones in town…Service was good, only bad side is they’re all the way in Tst.
Shisha for sale or just smoke  and do you ship to USA
Send to note be called Black Swan
